  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of the study is to determine the main factors contributing to predicted 10 year
      cardiovascular risk in an HIV infected cohort, and the role of anti-HIV drug use in altering
      this risk
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
